        class name:
            `class MyEvent(Event): ...`
            `MyEvent(key=value)`  # event_type == "MyEvent"
        Create a new event.
        
        - Base `Event` class: `Event("MyEvent", key=value)`
        - Subclasses: `MyEvent(key=value)` — event_type auto-set by `__init__`
